@namespace Miko.Ionic.Components
@inherits IonicComponentBase
@* Mirrors Ionic's <ion-avatar>: a circular inline-block container that clips its content
   (typically an <img> or <ion-img>) into a circle. It carries no intrinsic size — it sizes to
   its content. ios and md share the same geometry (50% radius + hidden overflow), so the mode
   class is stamped only for selector-parity with the rest of the component suite. *@
<div class="@($"{Mode} ion-avatar")">
    @ChildContent
</div>
